 "body_html": "<h1 class=\"heading heading-1 header-scroll\" align=\"\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"deterministic-wallet-formats\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\"><div id=\"section-deterministic-wallet-formats\" class=\"heading-anchor_backwardsCompatibility\"></div>Deterministic Wallet Formats</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Deterministic Wallet Formats\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-anchor\" href=\"#deterministic-wallet-formats\"></a></h1>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\" align=\"\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"type-1-single-chain-wallets\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\"><div id=\"section-type-1-single-chain-wallets\" class=\"heading-anchor_backwardsCompatibility\"></div>Type 1: Single Chain Wallets</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Type 1: Single Chain Wallets\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-anchor\" href=\"#type-1-single-chain-wallets\"></a></h2>\n<p>A Type 1 deterministic <span class=\"GlossaryItem-trigger\">wallet</span> is the simpler of the two, which can create a single series of keys from a single seed. A primary weakness is that if the seed is leaked, all funds are compromised, and wallet sharing is extremely limited.</p>\n<h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\" align=\"\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"type-2-hierarchical-deterministic-hd-wallets\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\"><div id=\"section-type-2-hierarchical-deterministic-hd-wallets\" class=\"heading-anchor_backwardsCompatibility\"></div>Type 2: Hierarchical Deterministic (HD) Wallets</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Type 2: Hierarchical Deterministic (HD) Wallets\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-anchor\" href=\"#type-2-hierarchical-deterministic-hd-wallets\"></a></h2>\n<p><span aria-label=\"Overview Of Hierarchical Deterministic Key Derivation\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"Overview Of Hierarchical Deterministic Key Derivation\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://dash-docs.github.io/img/dev/en-hd-overview.svg\" align=\"\" caption=\"\" height=\"auto\" title=\"\" width=\"auto\"/></span></span></p>\n<p>For an overview of the <span class=\"GlossaryItem-trigger\">HD wallet</span>, please see the <a href=\"core-guide-wallets\" target=\"\" title=\"\">developer guide section</a>.  For details, please see <a href=\"https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/blob/master/bip-0032.mediawiki\" target=\"\" title=\"\">BIP32</a>.</p>"
